sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  actor User as 用户
  participant Mobile as settlement 页面
  participant Api as SettlementsController
  participant Service as SettlementsService
  participant Energy as EnergyEntry 表
  participant Todo as Todo 表
  participant Settlement as WeeklySettlement 表
  participant Fruit as TreeFruit 表
  participant TreeApi as TreeController
  participant TreeService as TreeService

  User->>Mobile: 打开周结算并确认最终周结果
  Mobile->>Api: POST /settlements/weeks/:weekId
  Api->>Service: settleWeek(userId, weekId, finalScore, reflection)
  Service->>Energy: 读取本周每日能量记录
  Service->>Todo: 读取本周任务完成情况
  Service->>Service: 计算 suggestedScore 并生成 snapshotJson
  Service->>Settlement: upsert WeeklySettlement<br/>保存 finalScore / reflection / confirmedAt
  Service->>Fruit: create TreeFruit<br/>label / score / capsuleSummary
  Service-->>Api: settlement + fruit
  Api-->>Mobile: 周结算结果
  Mobile->>TreeApi: GET /tree/years/:year
  TreeApi->>TreeService: getYearTree(userId, year)
  TreeService->>Fruit: 读取年度果实列表
  TreeService->>Settlement: 读取结算关联信息
  TreeService->>TreeService: 按当前季度计算树阶段
  TreeService-->>TreeApi: stage / fruits / honors
  TreeApi-->>Mobile: 年度成长树数据
  Mobile-->>User: 展示新果实与时间胶囊
